40 class OmegaCE : public TransferModel
41 {
42 public:
43  OmegaCE(Mutation::Mixture& mix)
44  : TransferModel(mix)
45  {
46  mp_wrk1 = new double [mix.nSpecies()];
47  }
48 
49  ~OmegaCE()
50  {
51  delete [] mp_wrk1;
52  }
53 
54  double source()
55  {
56  static const double cv = 1.5*RU/mixture().speciesMw(0);
57  mixture().netProductionRates(mp_wrk1);
58  return mp_wrk1[0]*cv*mixture().Te();
59  }
60 
61 private:
62  double* mp_wrk1;
63 };
